21:44.484 --> 21:46.522
Even myself.

21:53.569 --> 21:56.107
You made me feel
like I wasn't alone anymore.

22:00.182 --> 22:02.420
God, I just...

22:02.453 --> 22:04.658
I've been alone for so long.

22:09.568 --> 22:11.639
(sniffles)

22:18.886 --> 22:20.924
(exhales)

22:28.005 --> 22:30.075
(sniffling)

22:59.568 --> 23:02.607
