26:22.239 --> 26:24.243
(chuckling softly)

26:25.880 --> 26:27.350
You're fucking deranged.

26:27.383 --> 26:29.120
I'm fucking deranged?
I'm fucking deranged?

26:29.153 --> 26:30.690
Listen.

26:30.723 --> 26:32.226
You can call me
whatever you want.

26:32.259 --> 26:34.965
But it won't change
the fact that you fucked me.

26:40.275 --> 26:42.312
And you liked that I was dead.

26:47.724 --> 26:49.794
Get the fuck off me.

26:50.763 --> 26:52.166
Okay, you're scared.

26:52.199 --> 26:53.402
I'm scared, too.

26:53.435 --> 26:56.308
Don't you see?

26:56.341 --> 26:58.412
Sam, Sam, there's no normal,

26:58.445 --> 27:00.382
