invaded your body,

29:06.502 --> 29:08.372
and now you're this girl
who likes pastels

29:08.405 --> 29:10.275
and afternoon tea.

29:10.308 --> 29:12.113
Where's my friend
with the rocking hair

29:12.146 --> 29:13.382
