to talk to dead people?

29:13.415 --> 29:14.985
Okay, that's not funny.

29:15.018 --> 29:17.356
I'm not joking.

29:18.425 --> 29:21.097
Are you sure you want
to do this?

29:21.130 --> 29:23.368
Jesse's a great guy, but...

29:23.401 --> 29:25.205
does he make you happy?

29:26.274 --> 29:28.444
Of course he makes me happy.
I...

29:30.282 --> 29:33.021
Look, this is, this is
what I want. I want...

29:33.054 --> 29:35.259
a white picket fence, 2.5 kids.

29:35.292 --> 29:38.165
I just want a boring,
regular life.

29:38.198 --> 29:41.538
You never gave a shit
about a boring, regular life.

29:42.874 --> 29:45.412
OFFICIANT:
We are gathered here today
to join this man

29:45.445 --> 29:48.385
and this woman
in holy matrimony.

29:48.418 --> 29:50.155
Jesse and Samantha

29:50.188 --> 29:52.527
have prepared their own vows

29:52.560 --> 29:54.498
to express their love.

29:54.531 --> 29:56.535
Samantha?

29:58.271 --> 30:00.275
Thank you.

30:01.578 --> 30:03.816
Jesse.
(chuckles)

30:05.920 --> 30:08.258
Growing up, I...

30:08.291 --> 30:10.295
didn't really have a family.

30:11.598 --> 30:14.170
And that was okay. I...

30:14.203 --> 30:16.374
learned to get through life
without one.

30:17.342 --> 30:19.313
But then I met you.

30:19.346 --> 30:21.084
You are...

30:21.117 --> 30:23.154
(sniffles)
...all I need.

30:24.958 --> 30:27.029
Sam...

30:27.062 --> 30:29.300
