I'm gonna marry that girl.

30:35.580 --> 30:37.583
You are the only one for me.

30:38.586 --> 30:41.291
And years from now,

30:41.324 --> 30:43.462
when we're surrounded
by our kids

30:43.496 --> 30:45.466
and our grandkids,

30:45.500 --> 30:47.604
we'll tell them about this day.

30:47.637 --> 30:50.209
And show them

30:50.242 --> 30:52.213
our story.

30:52.246 --> 30:55.085
This wasn't part of the program.

30:55.118 --> 30:57.957
(whispers): Sometimes
it can be fun to go off script.

31:02.266 --> 31:04.470
(laughter)

31:04.504 --> 31:06.575
WOMAN:
They're so cute.

31:15.125 --> 31:16.227
Is that Sam?

31:16.260 --> 31:17.597
POPPY:
Is that a dead body?

31:19.668 --> 31:22.206
-What is that?
-Jesse, you, uh, you...

31:22.239 --> 31:24.611
-Please tell me that's not you.
-Jesse, you-you don't,
you don't understand...

31:24.644 --> 31:26.615
He's never gonna
understand you, Sam.

31:26.648 --> 31:28.553
Look at what he's done.

31:28.586 --> 31:30.690
-Killed everything
special about you.
-Who the fuck is he?

31:30.723 --> 31:32.393
SAM: He, we-we used
to work together...

31:32.426 --> 31:34.363
That's the guy in the video.

31:34.396 --> 31:35.967
So it's not a dead body?

31:36.000 --> 31:37.971
No, no, he's not dead,
obviously.

31:38.004 --> 31:39.641
Look, this is, it's a sick joke.

31:39.674 --> 31:41.010
-This is all...
-Yeah, but you thought
I was dead.

31:41.043 --> 31:43.248
And I think
that gave you permission.

31:43.281 --> 31:45.620
The green light to be who you
really are, to want what you

31:45.653 --> 31:47.423
-really want, to be with me.
-He's-he's delusional.

31:47.456 --> 31:49.494
There's a tape, Sam!

31:50.696 --> 31:53.602
That's you climbing
on top of a corpse.

31:54.704 --> 31:56.675
Dead or not,
that's you fucking another guy.

31:56.708 --> 31:58.513
-Who are you?
-(stammers) Look,

31:58.546 --> 32:00.984
I-I was tricked.
This whole thing, it's a cr--

32:01.017 --> 32:03.154
-it's a crazy misunderstanding.
-Fuck you, Sam.

32:03.187 --> 32:05.192
-Jesse!
-(mutters)

32:05.225 --> 32:06.996
Jesse, I'm sorry!

32:07.029 --> 32:09.400
Jesse, stop. Jesse!

32:09.433 --> 32:11.672
-Sam, Sam, Sam! Stop, stop!
-Let fucking go of me! What?

32:11.705 --> 32:13.709
-You fucking filmed us?
-That is what it looks like

32:13.742 --> 32:15.513
to really be alive.

32:15.546 --> 32:17.283
♪ ♪

32:17.316 --> 32:19.655
This was the only way
I could save you.

32:19.688 --> 32:21.691
Because I love you.

32:22.760 --> 32:25.131
And I know you feel the same.

32:27.069 --> 32:29.675
No, I don't. I fucking hate you.

32:29.708 --> 32:32.012
Leave me the hell alone.

32:42.032 --> 32:43.569
Well, I can see you have a lot

32:43.602 --> 32:45.305
of experience in waste disposal.

32:45.338 --> 32:47.376
Yes, uh, I've handled every type

32:47.409 --> 32:48.779
of mess you can imagine.

32:48.812 --> 32:51.552
Um, for vomit,
sodium hypochlorite

32:51.585 --> 32:53.188
and kitty litter works best.

32:53.221 --> 32:55.660
For blood stains on the carpet,
the trick is

32:55.693 --> 32:58.064
sprinkle a little
potato starch actually.

32:58.097 --> 33:00.068
Most people don't even know
how to disinfect a toilet.

33:00.101 --> 33:02.741
Oh, that's easy, vinegar.

33:02.774 --> 33:05.613
Clearly, you can do the work.

33:05.646 --> 33:08.384
You know your way
around a dirty mess.

33:09.654 --> 33:11.759
Sorry, excuse me

33:11.792 --> 33:13.695
-one minute.
-Yeah.

33:23.582 --> 33:26.487
I, uh, apologize.

33:26.521 --> 33:28.358
It seems like
we just filled the position.

33:28.391 --> 33:30.763
Oh, um, well,
if anything opens up,

33:30.796 --> 33:32.466
I'm happy to take
the job nobody wants.

33:32.500 --> 33:33.836
I'm a very hard worker
and, um...

33:33.869 --> 33:36.374
Miss...

33:36.407 --> 33:38.244
we can't have a sex offender

33:38.277 --> 33:39.748
going into our clients' homes.

33:39.781 --> 33:41.752
No, I'm-I'm not, um...

33:41.785 --> 33:44.591
Look, I made one mistake.

33:44.624 --> 33:46.629
Haven't you ever made
a mistake in your life?

33:46.662 --> 33:48.331
I'm paying for it
every single day, please.

33:48.364 --> 33:50.302
I-I could really use the cash.

33:50.335 --> 33:52.339
Can you just give me a chance?
Um...

33:53.408 --> 33:55.445
♪ ♪

34:10.308 --> 34:12.345
(phone chimes)

34:21.397 --> 34:25.104
(distorted chatter, laughter)

34:30.716 --> 34:33.588
WOMAN:
Zombie fucker!

35:02.212 --> 35:04.249
♪ ♪

35:30.603 --> 35:32.640
You ruined my life.

35:36.848 --> 35:38.586
Sam...

35:38.619 --> 35:40.222
(drops shovel)

35:40.255 --> 35:41.692
Put the gun down.

35:41.725 --> 35:43.228
I get you're angry with me.

35:43.261 --> 35:44.463
Shut up.

35:46.668 --> 35:48.606
My friends won't talk
to me anymore.

35:48.639 --> 35:50.375
No one will hire me
'cause everyone thinks

35:50.408 --> 35:51.912
I'm a fucking sex offender,
when you're

35:51.945 --> 35:53.783
the one who lied.

35:53.816 --> 35:55.886
You tricked me.

35:56.888 --> 35:59.427
You took...

35:59.460 --> 36:01.463
everything.

36:02.633 --> 36:04.737
And now you get to just
keep living your best life?

36:06.675 --> 36:09.212
Hmm, it's just not right.

36:10.415 --> 36:11.785
You need to pay
for what you've done.

36:11.818 --> 36:13.989
Sam, I'm sorry.

36:14.022 --> 36:15.927
Please.

36:15.960 --> 36:17.396
We can talk rationally.

36:17.429 --> 36:19.534
This is not who you are.

36:19.567 --> 36:21.738
-I just want some answers.
-(scoffs)

36:21.771 --> 36:24.410
I just want to know why. What,
what did I do to deserve this?

36:24.443 --> 36:25.746
Why do you hate me
so fucking much?

36:25.779 --> 36:27.684
You idiot, I don't hate you!

36:27.717 --> 36:29.788
You were trapped!
I was trying to set you free!

36:29.821 --> 36:31.290
I didn't want any help!

36:31.323 --> 36:32.694
I never asked for it.
I was fine.

36:32.727 --> 36:34.564
No, you weren't!

36:36.300 --> 36:37.771
Fuck, Sam.

36:37.804 --> 36:40.910
The day my family died...

36:40.943 --> 36:43.516
I was so close to death,
I tasted it.

36:43.549 --> 36:44.918
I had their blood on me.

36:44.951 --> 36:47.289
And I...

36:47.322 --> 36:49.293
felt so alive.

36:49.326 --> 36:50.830
I was waking up
for the first time.

36:50.863 --> 36:52.901
Seeing the world
how it really was.

36:52.934 --> 36:54.436
No more pretending
everything's fine

36:54.469 --> 36:56.708
when the world's
not fucking fine.

36:56.741 --> 36:58.979
I thought
if I could give you that,

36:59.012 --> 37:01.317
a close brush with death,

37:01.350 --> 37:03.288
it would shock you awake.

37:03.321 --> 37:05.726
It was only supposed
to be for a few minutes.

37:05.759 --> 37:08.264
Just a jump start.

37:10.001 --> 37:12.707
But then you were crying.

37:12.740 --> 37:14.476
And you touched me.

37:15.946 --> 37:17.950
And I...

37:20.990 --> 37:22.994
I didn't want it to stop.

37:23.027 --> 37:25.431
I didn't want
to break the spell.

37:26.367 --> 37:28.004
I have never felt
that way before

37:28.037 --> 37:30.441
with anyone.

37:31.578 --> 37:33.481
You're psychotic.

37:33.515 --> 37:34.618
(scoffs)

37:34.651 --> 37:36.020
I don't need a man to tell me

37:36.053 --> 37:37.757
what I think
or what I really want.

37:37.790 --> 37:40.596
That is so goddamn patronizing.

37:40.629 --> 37:41.965
And I know about your mother.

37:45.506 --> 37:47.342
I swear to God,
if you say one fucking...

37:47.375 --> 37:49.079
Three days.

37:49.112 --> 37:51.618
She was dead for three days

37:51.651 --> 37:53.622
before they found you.

37:53.655 --> 37:56.628
For three days, you drank
your dead mother's milk.

37:56.661 --> 37:58.632
Shut the fuck up.

37:58.665 --> 38:00.736
You're disgusting.

38:01.738 --> 38:03.609
You're disgusting.

38:03.642 --> 38:05.513
And beautiful.

38:05.546 --> 38:07.517
And fucked up.

38:07.550 --> 38:09.721
And amazing.

38:09.754 --> 38:11.625
You are all those things,
all at the same time.

38:11.658 --> 38:13.027
And that's why I love you.

38:14.764 --> 38:16.768
I love you, Sam.

38:16.801 --> 38:19.339
You don't have to hide anymore.

38:20.074 --> 38:22.479
(sniffles)

38:22.513 --> 38:24.784
Let the real you out,
and tell me,

38:24.817 --> 38:27.021
what did it feel like, to taste
death for the first time?

38:33.969 --> 38:35.539
(sniffles)

38:35.572 --> 38:37.610
