38:40.114 --> 38:42.052
At first,
I thought she had just...

38:42.085 --> 38:44.122
bumped her head.

38:45.458 --> 38:47.462
And she was sleeping.

38:52.673 --> 38:54.678
I brushed her hair.

38:54.711 --> 38:57.382
I...

38:57.415 --> 38:59.452
I fed her cereal.

39:01.123 --> 39:03.662
Just Mama and me.

39:09.874 --> 39:12.680
It was the last time
I ever felt safe.

39:15.451 --> 39:18.424
(laughs) No wonder
I'm so screwed up, fuck.

39:19.527 --> 39:21.531
And I...

39:21.564 --> 39:24.402
I thought I would never
feel like that again.

39:27.543 --> 39:29.547
Until that night.

39:30.949 --> 39:32.820
Until I was with you.

39:32.853 --> 39:34.991
How fucked up is that?

39:35.024 --> 39:37.062
I get it.

39:37.095 --> 39:39.099
I get you.

39:41.236 --> 39:43.508
I will never judge you.

39:45.646 --> 39:47.617
You should've just
let me keep sleepwalking.

39:47.650 --> 39:49.987
I had forgotten I was broken.

39:52.158 --> 39:54.830
But now I see.

39:55.833 --> 39:57.704
I think what I really want
is to be dead

39:57.737 --> 39:59.707
and alive at the same time.

40:02.012 --> 40:04.049
And I can never have that.

40:05.986 --> 40:08.925
There's no way to put
the pieces back together.

40:15.506 --> 40:17.008
There's no hope for me.

40:18.077 --> 40:20.015
Sam.

40:20.048 --> 40:21.518
(sniffles)

40:21.551 --> 40:23.220
There's hope for us.

40:26.026 --> 40:28.632
I would do anything...

40:28.665 --> 40:31.037
to be with you.

40:31.070 --> 40:33.007
I would die a million times

40:33.040 --> 40:34.977
to be with you for a minute.

40:36.280 --> 40:38.619
For a thousand years.

40:38.652 --> 40:40.488
Forever.

40:42.827 --> 40:44.931
You really mean that, don't you?

40:44.964 --> 40:47.804
Your weird and my weird,

40:47.837 --> 40:49.907
we belong together.

40:51.310 --> 40:53.848
We can be happy.

40:55.118 --> 40:57.523
We can be happy?

41:14.791 --> 41:17.061
Let me make you happy.

41:18.799 --> 41:20.802
Yeah.

41:22.573 --> 41:24.610
I think you're
the only one that could.

41:27.248 --> 41:30.054
(gunshot)

41:58.778 --> 42:00.716
For a minute.

42:00.749 --> 42:02.987
For a thousand years.

42:03.020 --> 42:04.857
Forever.

42:07.228 --> 42:09.800
Forever.

42:15.144 --> 42:17.115
♪ ♪
